#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.165"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.165:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.165:0.2"
msgid "16. Nandikkhayavagga"
msgstr "16. The End of Relishing"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 165. Micchādiṭṭhipahānasutta → micchādiṭṭhippahānasuttaṃ (bj) | micchādiṭṭhi (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.165:0.3"
msgid "165. Micchādiṭṭhipahānasutta"
msgstr "165. Giving Up Wrong View"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.165:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe …"
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn35.165:1.2"
msgid "ekamantaṃ nisinno so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn35.165:1.3"
msgid "“kathaṃ nu kho, bhante, jānato kathaṃ passato micchādiṭṭhi pahīyatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sir, how does one know and see so that wrong view is given up?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.165:2.1"
msgid "“Cakkhuṃ kho, bhikkhu, aniccato jānato passato micchādiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, knowing and seeing the eye, sights, eye consciousness, and eye "
"contact as impermanent, wrong view is given up. …"

msgctxt "sn35.165:2.2"
msgid "Rūpe aniccato jānato passato micchādiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.165:2.3"
msgid "Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ aniccato jānato passato micchādiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.165:2.4"
msgid "Cakkhusamphassaṃ aniccato jānato passato micchādiṭṭhi pahīyati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.165:2.5"
msgid ""
"yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi aniccato jānato passato micchādiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""
"And also knowing and seeing the pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that "
"arises conditioned by mind contact as impermanent, wrong view is given up."

msgctxt "sn35.165:2.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhu, jānato evaṃ passato micchādiṭṭhi pahīyatī”ti."
msgstr "This is how to know and see so that wrong view is given up.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.165:2.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
